reviewText: The kids love these movies! So cute!
Very nice DvD great for the price I love it
My kids (6 and 8) love these movies, and I like that they are clean. Plus you can't beat the price. Cute dogs and Christmas - a winning combination.
Kids loved watching the series over the holidays

I remember DEAN CAIN  from his LOIS & CLARK Superman TV series. I've always enjoyed his acting,
and after seeing a preview trailer for ONE of these "THE DOG THAT SAVED..." movies I saw this triple-disc,
triple-feature and jumped on it.
